      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's probably just a migraine because i haven't slept much and i've been super stressed lately. i was thinking about just taking a bunch of ibuprofen and some extra sleep to see if it goes away. do you think a high dose of ibuprofen would help kill this headache faster?",
