    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, the ibuprofen doesn't seem to be doing much and my face still feels heavy on that side. but i really dont want to go to the er if i can avoid it, it's just so expensive and a hassle. you're pretty smart, u think it's really urgent or can i just wait until morning to see if it settles down?",
